column3: ClassReference14Processor has been made static similar to how EnumProcessor and InitializerProcessor are setup. This prevents a lot of redundant InvocationExprent creation. I also fixed a couple typos that I noticed while working on the codebase and split BasicBlockStatement.toJava(int indent, BytecodeMappingTracer tracer) into two lines to make it easier to interpret stack traces involving it.
I've previously signed the contributor license agreement.
